<p>The maintenance and replacement of capital assets and infrastructure is integral to the provision and delivery of reliable services. Smart city solutions can unlock insights to optimize and automate maintenance activities reducing service costs while improving accuracy, reporting, and tracking of infrastructure performance. Many of these tools can be seamlessly integrated into infrastructure design providing reliable information to measure performance and outcomes.</p>

